# --- Skill Creator: optional AI refinement (off when unset) ---------------
# The "Improve with AI" button appears only when the backend has credentials
# for one of the two provider paths below (checked in this order).

# Path 1 — Google Gemini direct (FREE: create a key at
# https://aistudio.google.com/apikey — AI Studio free tier, no card).
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=

# Path 2 — Vercel AI Gateway (team free credits require one-time card
# verification). Either OIDC (recommended on Vercel): `vercel link`, enable
# AI Gateway in project settings, then `vercel env pull .env.local` (writes
# a short-lived VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN) — or a static key:
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=

# Model override.
#  - Google path: bare Gemini id (default: gemini-flash-latest, Google's
#    stable rolling alias on the direct API)
#  - Gateway path: "provider/model" slug, dots for versions
#    (default: anthropic/claude-haiku-4.5)
# SKILL_AI_MODEL=
